---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';

const REPO = 'https://github.com/nino-chavez/blueprint-platform/blob/main';
---
<Layout title="Operate" description="Use it day-to-day. Merchant + subscriber playbooks.">
  <header class="mb-10 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-warning">Operate</p>
    <h1 class="mb-3 font-heading text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight">
      Use it day-to-day.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-contrast-500">
      Merchant onboarding, subscriber experience, dunning playbook, support runbooks — the operational layer for after the demo is over. <strong class="font-medium text-foreground">Currently the thinnest lane.</strong> Authored playbooks land here as ops scenarios graduate from <code class="font-mono text-xs">apps/demos/scripts/</code>.
    </p>
  </header>

  <section class="mt-10">
    <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">What's available today</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li class="flex items-baseline gap-3 rounded-lg border border-contrast-200 bg-background p-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide text-success-foreground">Available</span>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Demo storyboard — 17 scripted scenarios</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-contrast-500">Click-paths covering storefront + admin surfaces with per-surface status. Source: <code class="font-mono text-[11px]">apps/demos/scenarios.json</code>.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://subs-demos.pages.dev" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="shrink-0 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-brand hover:underline">open ↗</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8">
    <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">Planned playbooks</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-contrast-500">Promoted from <code class="font-mono text-xs">apps/demos/scripts/*.md</code> scenarios into structured guides as content matures.</p>
    <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-dashed border-contrast-300 bg-background p-4">
        <p class="mb-1 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide text-contrast-400">Planned</p>
        <p class="font-medium text-foreground">Merchant guide</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-contrast-500">Onboarding · plan design · dunning rules · refund flows · cancellation policies</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-dashed border-contrast-300 bg-background p-4">
        <p class="mb-1 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide text-contrast-400">Planned</p>
        <p class="font-medium text-foreground">Subscriber experience</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-contrast-500">Account portal · payment management · skip/swap/pause · cancel flows</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
